cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper deals with speech recognition, which is related to sound processing. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper involves natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a connectionist temporal classification (CTC) based end-to-end automatic speech recognition (ASR) model, which is a machine learning technique. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses electroencephalography (EEG) features, which are related to neural computing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper involves video processing, which is related to computer vision.
